---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
import CtaBlock from '../components/CtaBlock.astro';
---

<Base
  surface="dark"
  title="About"
  description="We started Purpose Brands because brilliant food, drink, and wellness brands deserve better than a spreadsheet-driven Amazon agency."
>
  {/* Intro */}
  <Section tone="dark">
    <div class="about-intro">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>We built the Amazon agency we wished existed.</h1>
      <div class="about-intro__body">
        <p>
          We started Purpose Brands because we kept seeing the same thing:
          brilliant brands with amazing products, getting a raw deal from Amazon
          agencies that didn't understand their world. Agencies that treated them
          like just another account. That spread themselves across every platform
          and gave nobody their full attention.
        </p>
        <p>
          We've spent 15+ years in food, drink, and wellness — from Moët Hennessy
          to indie kombucha brands. We know the margins are tight, Amazon can feel
          like a black box, and getting it right can genuinely transform your
          business. So we built the agency we wished existed.
        </p>
        <p>
          We called it Purpose Brands because we wanted to work with people who
          are building something that matters. And we're a Surfers Against Sewage
          Ocean Network member because we're based on the South Devon coast and
          protecting our waters isn't abstract for us — it's personal.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  {/* Phoebe */}
  <Section tone="dark">
    <article class="bio">
      <div class="bio__image" aria-hidden="true">
        <span>Phoebe</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bio__body">
        <p class="eyebrow">Founder</p>
        <h2>Phoebe Bocchinelli</h2>
        <p class="bio__lede">
          I've spent 15 years in consumer brands — ecommerce, sales, and marketing
          — with 6 of those specifically on Amazon Vendor and Seller across the UK
          and US.
        </p>
        <p>
          Before starting Purpose Brands, I worked with Moët Hennessy, Belvedere
          Vodka, Veuve Clicquot, and Heineken. I started this agency because I saw
          too many great brands being let down by agencies that didn't get their
          category. I'm based in South Devon, happiest near the sea, and I believe
          the best brands are the ones that stand for something.
        </p>
        <ul class="bio__trust" aria-label="Brands Phoebe has worked with">
          <li>Moët Hennessy</li>
          <li>Heineken</li>
          <li>Veuve Clicquot</li>
          <li>Belvedere Vodka</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </article>
  </Section>

  {/* Biraj */}
  <Section tone="dark">
    <article class="bio bio--reverse">
      <div class="bio__image" aria-hidden="true">
        <span>Biraj</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bio__body">
        <p class="eyebrow">Co-founder</p>
        <h2>Biraj Parmar</h2>
        <p class="bio__lede">
          8+ years in Amazon, Shopify, and ecommerce — from operations and
          strategy to PPC and SEO.
        </p>
        <p>
          I built my own Amazon and D2C business from scratch and sold it for
          seven figures in 2021 to Heroes Technology, then stayed on as an
          internal brand consultant. I've been on every side of Amazon — as a
          seller, a brand owner, and now as someone who helps other brands win. I
          know what works because I've done it myself.
        </p>
        <ul class="bio__trust" aria-label="Brands Biraj has worked with">
          <li>Heroes Technology</li>
          <li>Sports Laboratory</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </article>
  </Section>

  {/* Bottom CTA */}
  <Section tone="dark">
    <CtaBlock />
  </Section>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-intro {
    max-width: 56rem;
  }

  .about-intro h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-display-lg);
    max-width: 18ch;
    margin: 2rem 0 3rem;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .about-intro__body {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .about-intro__body p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(250, 250, 247, 0.78);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .bio {
    display: grid;
    gap: 3rem;
    padding-top: 4rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-hairline-dark);
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .bio {
      grid-template-columns: 5fr 7fr;
      gap: 5rem;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .bio--reverse .bio__image {
      order: 2;
    }
  }

  .bio__image {
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    background: rgba(250, 250, 247, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-hairline-dark);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    max-width: 420px;
  }

  .bio__image span {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: rgba(250, 250, 247, 0.35);
  }

  .bio__body h2 {
    margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .bio__lede {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.3;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    max-width: 38ch;
  }

  .bio__body > p {
    color: rgba(250, 250, 247, 0.75);
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .bio__trust {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 2rem 0 0;
    margin: 2rem 0 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-hairline-dark);
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.625rem 1rem;
  }

  .bio__trust li {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(250, 250, 247, 0.7);
    padding: 0.5rem 0.875rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-hairline-dark);
    border-radius: 999px;
  }
</style>
